ack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4tD","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32900,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/27\/not-true-muslim-indifferent\/","url_meta":{"origin":17213,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Duties: Mercy to children, respect to elders","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe is not one of us who is neither merciful to our young, nor respects the rights of our elders, nor enjoins good and forbids evil.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1921 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Suyuti\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29350,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/hadith-on-wisdom-no-wisdom-unless-one-has-experience-of-age\/","url_meta":{"origin":17213,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wisdom: No wisdom unless one has experience of age","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no forbearance unless one has blundered, and there is no wisdom unless one has experience.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2033 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12638,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/05\/grey-hairs-in-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":17213,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Elders: Gray hairs in Islam are a blessing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn 'Abasah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has grown a gray hair in the way of Allah, it will be a light for him on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1635 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirimdhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8528,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/18\/tongue-moist-dhikr-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":17213,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Keep your tongue always remembering Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Busr reported: A\u00a0man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, the laws of Islam are too many for me, so tell me something\u00a0I\u00a0can hold onto.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cKeep your tongue moist with the remembrance of Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3375 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35178,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/09\/honoring-leaders\/","url_meta":{"origin":17213,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Leaders: Honoring elders, scholars, righteous rulers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 9, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa al-Ash\u2019ari reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, part of glorifying Allah is to honor the gray-haired Muslim and the bearer of the Quran, who is neither extravagant nor neglectful of it, and to honor the just ruler.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31953,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/11\/blessings-with-your-elders\/","url_meta":{"origin":17213,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Shuyukh: Blessings are with your elders","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBlessings are with your elders.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 559 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u